Weapon Bond
	KEY:Weapon Bond ~ Magus
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural
	DESC:If you are bonded to a weapon through the arcane weapon class feature, you can call that weapon to your hand as a free action once per round. The weapon appears in your hand instantly, even if it is in the possession of another creature or on another plane of existence. This ability does not function in areas that prevent or block teleportation magic or planar travel. Alternatively, you can teleport to the nearest open square to your bonded weapon, as if using Greater Teleport, except that you cannot bring any other creatures with you. In addition, if the weapon is not in your possession, you can scry on it at will and any creature in possession of the item takes a -8 penalty on its saving throw to resist this scrying.
	SOURCEPAGE:p.5



